      Methods in com.spazedog.lib.rootfw3.extenders that return FilesystemExtender.MountStat 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      FilesystemExtender.MountStat[] FilesystemExtender.Filesystem.getFstabList()
      This will provide the same information as FilesystemExtender#getMountList() only this will not provide information about currently mounted file systems.
      FilesystemExtender.MountStat[] FilesystemExtender.Filesystem.getMountList()
      This will return a list of all currently mounted file systems, with information like device path, mount location, file system type and mount options.
      FilesystemExtender.MountStat FilesystemExtender.Device.statFstab()
      This is the same as FilesystemExtender#getFstabList(), only this method will just return the mount information for this specific device or mount location.
      FilesystemExtender.MountStat FilesystemExtender.Device.statMount()
      This is the same as FilesystemExtender#getMountList(), only this method will just return the mount information for this specific device or mount location.
